OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread northeast this evening,
OL,7,Falthough light and patchy in the east.
OL,8,FFurther outbreaks of rain overnight,
OL,9,Fmainly across the west where it will
OL,10,Fturn persistent later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain will clear
OL,13,Faway northeast through the morning.
OL,14,FThen turning brighter with scattered
OL,15,Fshowers, occasionally heavy in the
OL,16,Fwest later. Fresh to strong
OL,17,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
