OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with showers on Saturday, windy
OL,7,Fat first. Drier on Sunday but still a
OL,8,Ffew light showers around. Chance of
OL,9,Fsome showery rain on Monday.
